{"id": "1511735216186593540", "channel_id": "1511380800606703786", "type": 0, "author_id": "819349396789526619", "author_name": "tajimal_drawing", "author_bot": false, "content": "俺は深海界域を極めようと思う\n難しいこと考えるのは苦手なんだ\n詰まったらそれはその時考えればいいよね", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T14:16:02.221000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "suki", "emoji_id": "1390952965006819539", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "realm_aequor", "emoji_id": "1437283645051375777", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1511380800606703786", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸々の備忘録", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1511586558002724957", "channel_id": "1510911214346305566", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻夢ゴリアテで沙耶試運転。\nルート間違えて一戦多く戦闘。\nとはいえ23ターンもかかる。\n\nオルラ使い始めた頃の使いこなせてない感を思い出す。", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T04:25:19.348000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1511586557482766396", "filename": "IMG_8245.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 610655, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511586557482766396/IMG_8245.png?ex=6a33732f&is=6a3221af&hm=04284196a64425d289748cff0dda39bbebdfee4d45000e426def251e8bd4a623&"}, {"id": "1511586557771911291", "filename": "IMG_8246.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 389536, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511586557771911291/IMG_8246.png?ex=6a33732f&is=6a3221af&hm=62b2d3626b3ba1aa2571edf611d2db674ebb9199eaa7bdfc49f110df9d047d7c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510911214346305566", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "ニムフィーアの毒パ研究日誌", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1511666431106879660", "channel_id": "1510911214346305566", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "沙耶イベスト高難度\n試しに3枚カード引っ張るキーオーダー\nカードの巡りがメチャクチャ早いが、ライカーのバフとのタイミング合わせが難しかったり、黒沼の回数減って忍耐貯めれなかったりで課題も多い。", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T09:42:42.580000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1511666430679056414", "filename": "IMG_8248.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 594511, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511666430679056414/IMG_8248.png?ex=6a33bd92&is=6a326c12&hm=156363f8c1619daba381bcdc01bd1efee85521582994933fac72813167b37c40&"}, {"id": "1511666431052480592", "filename": "IMG_8249.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 383511, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511666431052480592/IMG_8249.png?ex=6a33bd92&is=6a326c12&hm=7122ee5ef6c08440469a33774e960503ce1f64961eaa0730fe4b275bd5471916&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510911214346305566", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "ニムフィーアの毒パ研究日誌", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1511694042474348664", "channel_id": "1510911214346305566", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻夢カエクス\n慣れないことし過ぎて崩壊\n22ターン\n沙耶にリリー紀行札つけてみたけど一度も夢遊の異界使う暇もなく完全に無駄でした。ゆっくり進められるイベストとかならまだ良さそう。幻夢では二度とつけない。\n\nキーオーダーもやっぱりリリーなのか…？もしかしてベストな4人目はライカーじゃないのか？\n\n沙耶を使うたびにどんどんよく分からなくなってくる", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T11:32:25.643000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1511694041476104324", "filename": "IMG_8251.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 610904, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511694041476104324/IMG_8251.png?ex=6a33d749&is=6a3285c9&hm=4cf8fb3f876adb70ef038e87be13e97dc580cf5788142a2e5a83a7cdd633e5cc&"}, {"id": "1511694042042339368", "filename": "IMG_8250.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 389980, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1511694042042339368/IMG_8250.png?ex=6a33d749&is=6a3285c9&hm=c429371010d20bfcbb0c10d44eda842f4ef27e90c6152a21263a6ab1d9c922c0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510911214346305566", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "ニムフィーアの毒パ研究日誌", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
